SUMMARY:Easter: Kids Colouring Activity
DESCRIPTION:Calling all young artists! Grab your favourite Easter designs\, get creative\, and have a hoppin’ good time! 🎨\n\n\n\n\n\n🐣 Colouring Sheets and instructions will be released on Friday\, March 6th. \n🥚Pick up a sheet at BCU Financial (2280 Bloor St W) or\, download from here!\n🥚Return your completed sheet to BCU Financial by Friday\, March 27.\n🥚Enjoy the bunny’s artwork on BCU’s window and claim your prizes during the Easter Hop and Hunt event on April 4th\n🎁 Every child who enters gets a prize!\n \n\nThank you to our Sponsors BCU Financial and Neighbur for supporting this activity 
URL:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/event/easter-community-colouring-event-activity/
LOCATION:Bloor West Village\, Bloor Street West and Willard Avenue (South side of the Street)\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6S 1P4\, Canada
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/svg+xml:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Colouring-Acitivity.svg
ORGANIZER;CN="Bloor West Village BIA":MAILTO:info@bloorwestvillagebia.com
END:VEVENT
