SUMMARY:Easter Scavenger Hunt!
DESCRIPTION: 🐰 Bunnies are hopping back into Bloor West Village! ✨\nJoin us for a FREE day of family fun on Saturday\, April 4th\, from 10 AM – 2 PM. \nBring the whole family for a magical spring outing—meet the Easter Bunny and friends\, then take part in our interactive scavenger hunt! Visit local businesses\, search for hidden bunnies and eggs\, and discover everything the neighbourhood has to offer. \n🎯 Complete 10 stops to be entered to win exciting prizes✨ Visit more locations for bonus entries⭐ Don’t miss our Golden Stops for extra fun and surprises \nKeep an eye out—some locations may have bonus treats and special offers along the way! \n🐣 Coming Soon: Watch for the official registration link and check-in locations.
URL:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/event/2026-easter-scavenger-hunt/
LOCATION:Bloor West Village\, Bloor Street West and Willard Avenue (South side of the Street)\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6S 1P4\, Canada
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.bloorwestvillagebia.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/DSC03460-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Bloor West Village BIA":MAILTO:info@bloorwestvillagebia.com
END:VEVENT
